{"tid":2139683,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"英國england chavs會5會打7BNO榮光香港人？","createTime":"2020-08-04T12:31:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T17:07:13.000Z","uid":277010,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"62db2634b3320b1f5f7c988c8f8b13c04839a766","tid":2139683,"uid":277010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T12:31:10.000Z","msg":"亞洲會有「那個病」都是因為太落後&hellip;被吐口水、強迫停學，揭武漢肺炎風暴歐洲激烈排華原因-風傳媒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國的排華情況在england chavs群體(大概是香港的童黨，一般指15至20多yr的英國小混混，一般也是三，五成群，無個好人)，專在學校，車站，快餐店，酒店，球埸欺負亞洲華人，小則吐口水，被抛垃圾，口言咒罵，重則拳打腳踢，偷錢搶手機。<br />\n<br />\n如果有錢住zone 1上等白人區當然少遇上england chavs,但如果是窮的華人，住着D窮人白人區，就成日會遇上chavs,不知哪天遇上一班失業，失學的chavs，怪罪華人帶武肺入英國，慘成出氣袋。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.storm.mg/lifestyle/2265534?page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.storm.mg%2Flifestyle%2F2265534%3Fpage%3D1&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd%2Bu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=a4a6f3bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.storm.mg/lifestyle/2265534?page=1</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wVq8DS5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwVq8DS5.jpg&h=4f96a543&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0R3FuZM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0R3FuZM.jpg&h=8f701706&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ovxV3jN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FovxV3jN.jpg&h=51352eed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EyTRBEO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEyTRBEO.jpg&h=4c9d1f2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XZBr9ZP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXZBr9ZP.jpg&h=2e9363a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OBQ1erw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOBQ1erw.jpg&h=9e76ed6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.